    "itemKey": "",
    "description": "<p><strong>Trigger:</strong> A target within range fails a Check.</p><p><strong>Reaction:</strong> Make a Spell Check against the target’s Repeated Charisma Save.</p><p><strong>Save Failure:</strong> The target is Taunted by you for the duration.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Spell Enhancements</span></strong></span></p><p><strong>Tunnel Vision: (1 MP)</strong> While Taunted by this Spell, the target can’t willingly move away from you.</p><p><strong>Blinding Rage: (2 MP)</strong> While Taunted by this Spell, the target is Blinded and Deafened to all creatures except you.</p>",
